    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Anxiety
---
Loss gives rise to anxiety when the loss is either impending or thought to
be temporary. Anxiety contains a kernel of hope. But when lossappears to be
permanent, anxiety -- protest -- gives way to depression -- despair.
